{"tid":1076570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心動！只要台幣3萬6　跟高橋聖子2天1夜泡湯行","createTime":"2019-03-25T02:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T11:31:02.000Z","uid":32511,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"070705c7f9a4d7b56fbfd087c643d51083e4e0fc","tid":1076570,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"日本人氣AV女優高橋聖子推出二天一夜旅行團，讓粉絲跟她一起泡溫泉。<br />\n<br />\n高橋聖子在《推特》分享限定40人參加的泡湯攝影二天一夜旅行團資訊，團費12萬9600日圓(36000新台幣)包含巴士、住宿、用餐、保險等費用，預定4月20日東京新宿出發。<br />\n<br />\n這個巴士兩天一夜旅行行程，除了可以跟高橋聖子採草莓、泡湯拍照，還能一起享用豪華晚宴野球拳大會，而且沒有限定日本人參加，但至少要能夠理解行程中工作人員的日文指示。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EosK9sk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEosK9sk.jpg&h=cfd3058f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrXCK0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrXCK0G.jpg&h=cf128cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3aMDkG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3aMDkG.jpg&h=911d180a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2c3FHNm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2c3FHNm.jpg&h=21a69fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZ2vky2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZ2vky2.jpg&h=4e1ecf32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLHjdT2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLHjdT2.jpg&h=1c8e4895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dcRDusn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdcRDusn.jpg&h=d908afc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b596657da9dca3ae86aaac77329e55bbe04d119","tid":1076570,"uid":9470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"感謝宴"},{"pid":"1f1738288aca4e232b485ca5149849b67042c247","tid":1076570,"uid":2404,"like":2,"d